92,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776154374281,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/d3be1be3-1f87-460b-a058-5a6897dce083.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compare the current session state against the heartbeat state.\n\n**Last heartbeat state (12:43 UTC):**\n- cron:ed2d0b5d (5p QLHV): running ✅\n- cron:6f3323ef (5p DTLX): running ✅\n- telegram:group:-5163901258: running ✅\n- telegram:group:-5168104492: done ✅\n- telegram:direct:6053576134: done ✅\n- main: done ✅\n- cron:e7885813 (Agent Status): running ✅ (stale)\n\n\n- cron:b653a6c0 (QLHV Report): stale zombie ✅\n- cron:ac986a8d (Telegram delivery retry): done ✅ (cleaned up)\n\nLooking at the live sessions now, I can see the QLHV and DTLX cron jobs are still running, the agent status cron is active but stale, the QLHV report cron is a pre-existing zombie, and the telegram delivery retry cron is still in the list.\n\nChecking the actual status: both 5p cron monitors are running, the agent status cron is executing with a \"Agent Status to Lead\" label, the QLHV report cron remains a stale zombie with no recent activity, and the Telegram delivery retry cron has ended. Now I'm comparing this against the last heartbeat state to see if anything has shifted. The main changes I'm seeing are that the QLHV report cron is still stale but hasn't progressed, and the Telegram delivery cron has moved to done status while the Agent Status cron has become stale. Comparing against the last report timestamp of 12:13 UTC, the stale cron statuses haven't changed since the 12:43 UTC heartbeat, and the delivery retry session is still present in the sessions list. I'm seeing the 5p QLHV cron is running, which is a new state, but that's just a process detail for monitoring purposes rather than an actual ecosystem event I need to broadcast. Since the heartbeat state matches and the pipeline is stable, I should stay silent and not send a report.\n\nNow I'm updating the heartbeat state to mark the new cron IDs and timestamps."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current state against `heartbeat-state.json`:\n\n- **cron:ed2d0b5d** (5p QLHV): still running ✅\n- **cron:6f3323ef** (5p DTLX): still running ✅\n- **telegram:group:-5163901258**: still running ✅\n- **cron:e7885813** (Agent Status): still stale (pre-existing) ✅\n- **cron:b653a6c0** (QLHV Report): still stale zombie ✅\n- **cron:ac986a8d**: done/cleaned ✅\n\nNo new changes detected since last stable heartbeat. Silent exit.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bmsy5plfsneu_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"lastHeartbeat\": \"2026-04-14T12:46:00Z\",\n  \"lastReport\": \"2026-04-14T12:13:00Z\",\n  \"lastReportDelivered\": false,\n  \"silentExit\": true,\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report (QLHV)\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T12:46:00Z\", \"updatedAt\": 1776170845566 },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T12:46:00Z\", \"updatedAt\": 1776170596777 },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"QLHV Ecosystem Group\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T12:14:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"DTLX Ecosystem Group\", \"endedAt\": \"2026-04-14T10:55:00Z\", \"lastSeen\": \"2026-04-14T12:46:00Z\" },\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"Lead Direct Session\", \"endedAt\": \"2026-04-14T10:42:00Z\", \"lastSeen\": \"